  "detailed_description": "<h1>More Games X1 Studio</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Solve puzzles, destroy bombs, dodge obstacles, face dangers, find keys to open all doors and return home.<br>15 levels in 5 different scenarios.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/975607e9654aa2b191012f9ad8d34568.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/975607e9654aa2b191012f9ad8d34568.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/975607e9654aa2b191012f9ad8d34568.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Solve the puzzles.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Courage</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/f881e48e9d67af9c76a17602b8e22753.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/f881e48e9d67af9c76a17602b8e22753.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/f881e48e9d67af9c76a17602b8e22753.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Have no fear.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dangers</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/79178f7791096e88035adb55f760f02d.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/79178f7791096e88035adb55f760f02d.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/79178f7791096e88035adb55f760f02d.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Face the dangers.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obstacles</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/06865f37d93eedc7ae7bdc361e019601.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/06865f37d93eedc7ae7bdc361e019601.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/06865f37d93eedc7ae7bdc361e019601.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Overcome obstacles.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanisms</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/10b1abc315fa85ce1faafc83c5079849.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/10b1abc315fa85ce1faafc83c5079849.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/10b1abc315fa85ce1faafc83c5079849.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Scenario interaction.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy the Bombs</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/5ca84ce70b3290167ebcdc2e4bce0884.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/5ca84ce70b3290167ebcdc2e4bce0884.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/5ca84ce70b3290167ebcdc2e4bce0884.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Destroy the bombs using the stones on the way.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find the Keys</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/1bd09d3ddda050f3d770d3dbc608ad9a.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/1bd09d3ddda050f3d770d3dbc608ad9a.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/1bd09d3ddda050f3d770d3dbc608ad9a.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Each level has 6 lost keys.<br><br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exit</h2></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/d46ec8ef0b8f746ba27c6f3091a71b0b.poster.avif?t=1646582721\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/d46ec8ef0b8f746ba27c6f3091a71b0b.webm?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375640/extras/d46ec8ef0b8f746ba27c6f3091a71b0b.mp4?t=1646582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Open the last door.",
